                  üí¨ Explore Coaching
                </a>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-monica-teal px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg border-2 border-monica-teal hover:bg-monica-teal hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
                  üìû Free Consultation
